source.name: Natural Hazards Data and Information Viewer
source.description: The Natural Hazards Data and Information Viewer provides web map-based discovery, descriptions, and download capability for the global database of historical tsunamis, earthquakes, volcanoes, and other associated data at NOAA's National Geophysical Data Center.
